Bluetooth-Frwk-NG - BlueZ framework new generation
**************************************************


Copyright (C) 2013-2014 Intel Corporation

Compilation and installation
============================

In order to compile Bluetooth-Frwk-NG you need following software packages:
	- CMake tool
	- GCC compiler
	- D-Bus library
	- glib-2.0 library
	- gio-2.0 library
	- gio-unix-2.0 library

To compile:
	cmake . && make

To run:
	sudo cp packaging/bluetooth-service.conf packaging/bluezlib.conf packaging/bluez-lib-test.conf packaging/bluezobex.conf /etc/dbus-1/system.d/
	./src/bluetooth-service

To test API (select one to test the corresponding API):
	./test/bluez-capi-test
	./test/bluez-lib-test
	./test/obex-lib-test
	./test/bt-serivce-lib-test

